## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="871f2-127">下面的示例创建的应用程序返回有关服务总线快速信息语法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="871f2-127">The following example creates a grammar for an application that returns information about bus shuttle service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="871f2-128">第一种方法， `GrammarUrlForRoute`，采用字符串，它指定一个路由，并将其追加到一个字符串，指定的语法的位置。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="871f2-128">The first method, `GrammarUrlForRoute`, takes a string that specifies a route and appends it to a string specifying the location of a grammar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="871f2-129">这将在该语法中指定特定的规则。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="871f2-129">This specifies a particular rule in that grammar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="871f2-130">该方法返回`Uri`该规则。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="871f2-130">The method returns a `Uri` for that rule.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="871f2-131">第二种方法， `CreateGrammarForRoute`，创建<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>元素名为`grammar`与指定的规则引用`Uri`传递给它的`GrammarUrlForRoute`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="871f2-131">The second method, `CreateGrammarForRoute`, creates an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> element named `grammar` with a rule reference specified by the `Uri` passed to it by `GrammarUrlForRoute`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="871f2-132">请注意，变量名为 _route 封闭类的成员。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="871f2-132">Note that the variable named _route is a member of an enclosing class.</span></span>  

```  
private Uri GrammarUrlForRoute(string route)  
{  
  return new Uri("http://localhost/MyBus/MyBusLocations.grxml#LocationsForRoute" + route);  
}  

private SrgsDocument CreateGrammarForRoute()  
{  
  SrgsDocument grammar = new SrgsDocument();  
  grammar.Mode = SrgsGrammarMode.Voice;  
  SrgsRule rule = new SrgsRule("LocationsForRoute" + _route);  
  SrgsRuleRef ruleref = new SrgsRuleRef(GrammarUrlForRoute(_route));  

  SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag tag = new SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag ("$.Location = $$");  

  rule.Elements.Add(ruleref);  
  rule.Elements.Add(tag);  
  grammar.Rules.Add(rule);  
  grammar.Root = rule;  
  return grammar;  
}  
```  

> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="871f2-133">名为 _ 变量`route`是未声明和在前面的示例未定义。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="871f2-133">The variable named _`route` is undeclared and undefined in the preceding sample.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="871f2-134">它应声明为<xref:System.String>和包含为特定的总线路由的路由数目之前编译并运行上面的示例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="871f2-134">It should be declared as a <xref:System.String> and contain the route number for a particular bus route before the preceding sample is compiled and run.</span></span>



